cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.IR 

This paper deals with learning representations from electronic health records (EHR) data, which is a common task in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves data management and analysis, which could fall under cs.DB (Databases) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with medical concepts and their representation, which could be categorized under cs.CY (Computational Biology and Bioinformatics).
